**the system only sample them within the same island:**

```python
# openevolve/database.py (ProgramDatabase._sample_inspirations)

# Get the island where the parent resides
parent_island = parent.metadata.get("island", self.current_island)

# Only retrieve code from this specific island to use as reference context for mutation
island_program_ids = list(self.islands[parent_island])
island_programs = [self.programs[pid] for pid in island_program_ids if pid in self.programs]
